p: In the case of MDA-MB-231, a dose and time-dependent inhibitory effect was also detected in ethanol extract- and methanol extract-treated cells ( Figure 6D, 6E). For the ethanolic extract, the IC 50 was 375.6 μg/ml after 24 h, 211.5 μg/ml after 48 h, and 126.3 μg/ml after 72 h ( Figure 6D). For the methanolic extract, the IC 50 value exhibited 254.8 μg/ml after 24 h, 167.1 μg/ml after 48 h, and 90.43 μg/ml after 72 h ( Figure 6E). The aqueous extract showed no inhibitory effect on cell viability during the time course ( Figure 6F).
